OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Health and Science
OL,7,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,9,FBeneath the mountains at the Swiss-
OL,10,FFrench border, as deep as 175 metres
OL,11,Fbelow ground, lies the Large Hadron
OL,12,FCollider ` the world's biggest and
OL,13,Fmost powerful particle accelerator.
OL,15,FIt's a 27-kilometre ring where beams
OL,16,Fof particles are fired at each other
OL,17,Fat nearly the speed of the light.
