OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FWhen they collide, they break up into
OL,7,Fsmaller particles that scientists
OL,8,Fanalyse in the hope of making new
OL,9,Fdiscoveries about how the universe
OL,10,Fworks ` including what happened just
OL,11,Fafter the Big Bang.
OL,13,FIt's the largest physics experiment in
OL,14,Fthe world, but scientists want to make
OL,15,Fit even bigger.
OL,17,FThey want to build the Future Circular
OL,18,FCollider ` it would be more than three
OL,19,Ftimes longer than the current tunnel
OL,20,Fat 91 kilometres.
