OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FEurope is currently the world leader
OL,7,Fin particle physics ` but China is
OL,8,Fsnapping at its heels with its own
OL,9,Fplans for a an even bigger and more
OL,10,Fpowerful giant collider called the
OL,11,FCircular Electron Positron Collider.
OL,13,FIt would be just as big as the
OL,14,Fproposed new European collider and
OL,15,Fwould challenge European supremacy in
OL,16,Fparticle physics.
OL,18,FIt could begin building as early as
OL,19,F2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
