OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FThe new director general in waiting of
OL,7,FCERN is British scientist Professor
OL,8,FMark Thomson. He will take over
OL,9,Fofficially in January 2026.
OL,11,FOne of his biggest tasks will be
OL,12,Fconvincing European governments to
OL,13,Ffund the new collider at CERN at a
OL,14,Fcost of #13 billion.
OL,16,F"This is spread over 15 years not a
OL,17,Fone-off spend, and it is shared
OL,18,Fbetween 24 member states of CERN and
OL,19,Fother international partners,"
OL,20,FProfessor Thompson said.
