OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,F"To convince the government there are
OL,7,Fmany arguments. One is the science,
OL,8,Fand you have to base why you're doing
OL,9,Fit on the science. Then there is the
OL,10,Fwider economic impact of working right
OL,11,Fat the forefront of science and
OL,12,Ftechnology which will then filter down
OL,13,Finto the economy," he added.
OL,15,FThe Large Hadron Collider (LHC) is
OL,16,Fcurrently in shutdown for maintenance
OL,17,Fand the High Luminosity upgrade.
OL,19,FThis will increase the brightness of
OL,20,Fthe collisions by ten times, meaning
OL,21,Fthere will also be ten times more data.
