OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FHowever, after this upgrade, the LHC
OL,7,Fwill be nearing its limit on how much
OL,8,Ffurther the science can be pushed with
OL,9,Fthe current equipment.
OL,11,FProfessor Thompson said the new
OL,12,Fcollider will be necessary in order to
OL,13,Fcontinue groundbreaking research.
OL,15,FIf China build its large collider and
OL,16,FEurope does not, there is a risk that
OL,17,Ftalent will also be lost as scientists
OL,18,Fgo to work in Asia instead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
