OL,3,CThe #13 billion race to build the next
OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,F"I think there's an argument that we
OL,7,Freally have to stay at that forefront
OL,8,Fbecause it really is one of the few,
OL,9,Fvery few areas where we have the lead
OL,10,Fin Europe compared to other parts of
OL,11,Fthe world," he said.
OL,13,FAt the end of March, CERN released a
OL,14,F"feasibility report" outlining how
OL,15,Fthis project would work and the
OL,16,Fpracticality of its construction.
