OL,4,Cparticle collider
OL,6,FNo fewer than 100 scenarios were
OL,7,Fdeveloped and analysed before settling
OL,8,Fon the preferred option ` a ring
OL,9,Fcircumference of around 90 kilometres
OL,10,Fat an average depth of 200 metres,
OL,11,Fwith eight surface sites and four
OL,12,Fexperiments.
OL,14,FCERN works on an open data principle,
OL,15,Fallowing scientists around the world
OL,16,Fto benefit from its data.
OL,18,FThere is a possibility that China
OL,19,Fwould not share all the data from its
OL,20,Fcollider, meaning access to new
OL,21,Ffindings could be restricted.
